data.title: James Cronin Service Details - Scottsville, New York
data.meta_description: Jim Cronin  PITTSFORD - August 10, 2018 at age 61. He is survived by his wife, Sharon Cronin; daughters, Susan Cronin, Kathleen (Brian) Delameter; sister, Joyce Cronin; granddaughters, Alida and Ellie Delameter. Arrangements by J.H. Cameron Funeral Home, Scottsville.
data.text:
Order Flowers

Ordering flowers from our site ensures that your order will reach us or the family in a timely manner, and your gesture of support will remain acknowledged in the Book of Memories for future generations. We thank you for helping to support the family during their time of need, and will fondly remember your kind gesture.
